to anyone?

27:47.056 --> 27:48.231
- I'm not proud of that.

27:48.275 --> 27:49.668
- [chuckles]

27:49.711 --> 27:52.714
You have a lot
not to be proud of, Mr. Varick.

27:52.758 --> 27:55.325
Enough to make up charges
like this to save your own ass?

27:55.369 --> 27:57.937
- Objection.
- Withdrawn.

27:57.980 --> 27:59.895
Nothing further.

28:01.462 --> 28:02.855
- Detective Rollins and I

28:02.898 --> 28:06.380
posed as a mixed-ethnicity,
interreligious couple.

28:06.423 --> 28:08.991
We were hoping to draw
Mr. O'Toole's attention,

28:09.035 --> 28:10.340
which we did.

28:10.384 --> 28:11.951
- Did he do
follow-up interviews?

28:11.994 --> 28:16.520
- Not with me, but he asked for
a private, nighttime meeting

28:16.564 --> 28:19.698
with Detective Rollins
in his minivan.

28:19.741 --> 28:22.570
- Thank you, Sergeant Khaldun.

28:22.613 --> 28:26.922
- So you lied
to a fellow officer

28:26.966 --> 28:30.186
about your religion,

28:30.230 --> 28:35.191
