28:43.373 --> 28:45.724
- I believe he thought
our marriage was real,

28:45.767 --> 28:48.204
but the red flags it raised
gave him leverage

28:48.248 --> 28:50.380
to sexually extort
Detective Rollins.

28:50.424 --> 28:52.643
- [scoffs]
You mean your fake wife.

28:52.687 --> 28:56.038
So your testimony is that
you're a good enough liar

28:56.082 --> 28:59.302
