in any way?

29:33.902 --> 29:36.122
- No, but his intent
was clear and graphic.

29:36.165 --> 29:37.732
He said we needed to go
to the back of the van

29:37.776 --> 29:38.994
where there was a mattress.

29:39.038 --> 29:40.996
- And did you go
to the back of the van?

29:41.040 --> 29:43.172
- No, my support team
pulled open the doors

29:43.216 --> 29:44.434
before that could happen.

29:44.478 --> 29:45.784
- So isn't it possible
he was testing you

29:45.827 --> 29:49.091
to see if you were really
a faithful wife?

29:49.135 --> 29:50.919
- Please.
