30:38.358 --> 30:39.881
- She tell her husband yet?

30:39.925 --> 30:41.840
- [sighs]

30:43.363 --> 30:44.668
There she is.

30:44.712 --> 30:45.974
Hey.

30:46.018 --> 30:47.410
- Ms. Benson,
