31:02.556 --> 31:06.386
- I can't, I'm sorry.
- Why?

31:08.562 --> 31:11.695
- I just found out
I'm pregnant.

31:11.739 --> 31:14.220
I'm praying this baby
looks like Joe.

31:14.263 --> 31:17.876
This is not about O'Toole
or any these women anymore.

31:17.919 --> 31:22.837
My baby needs a father,
and if Joe thinks for a second

31:22.881 --> 31:25.622
that this might be
O'Toole's baby?

31:25.666 --> 31:28.321
He could never know.

31:28.364 --> 31:30.540
[sniffles]

31:34.196 --> 31:34.370
.

31:34.414 --> 31:36.155
- Our scheduled witness
is not available

31:36.198 --> 31:37.330
at this time, Your Honor.

31:37.373 --> 31:38.157
We move for a continuance.
- Objection.

31:38.200 --> 31:39.985
I have a defense prepared.

31:40.028 --> 31:42.030
I'd like to move ahead
with my case.

31:42.074 --> 31:43.902
- How long do you need,
Mr. Carisi?

31:43.945 --> 31:45.947
- A few days, Your Honor.

31:45.991 --> 31:47.731
- I'll give you
till 9:00 a.m. tomorrow.

31:47.775 --> 31:49.124
- At which time,

31:49.168 --> 31:51.518
if there is no further
prosecution witnesses,

31:51.561 --> 31:53.389
we'll be moving ahead
for a dismissal.

31:53.433 --> 31:56.218
- Don't get ahead of yourself,
Mr. Buchanan.

31:59.221 --> 32:02.007
- Should've taken the deal,
Detective Carisi.

32:02.050 --> 32:04.835
[chuckles]

32:04.879 --> 32:05.836
- Lina backed out?

32:05.880 --> 32:07.447
- She's pregnant.

32:07.490 --> 32:10.189
- I get it.
That changes everything.

32:10.232 --> 32:13.235
- Yeah, it means
O'Toole's gonna walk.

32:13.279 --> 32:15.368
- What about Rosamie Klein?

32:15.411 --> 32:17.500
- You heard her; she doesn't
want to hurt her husband.

32:17.544 --> 32:21.026
- Maybe I can talk to him.
Jew to Jew.

32:21.069 --> 32:23.202
- You're Jewish?
- On my mother's side.

32:23.245 --> 32:25.726
Part Muslim on my father's.
It's a long story.

32:25.769 --> 32:28.511
- Sounds like everybody
in New York has one of those.

32:28.555 --> 32:30.209
- You want to take a ride
to Ocean Parkway,

32:30.252 --> 32:31.775
talk to the Kleins?

32:31.819 --> 32:35.214
- As my Baptist grandmama would
say, it's worth a Hail Mary.

32:37.912 --> 32:39.131
[knock on door]

32:40.175 --> 32:41.698
Hey.
Hey, Rosamie.

32:41.742 --> 32:43.004
