34:22.756 --> 34:24.323
[speaks Hebrew]

34:25.802 --> 34:26.847
- [speaks Hebrew]

34:26.890 --> 34:28.196
- Mm-hmm.

34:30.155 --> 34:33.027
- You, uh...

34:33.071 --> 34:34.507
