34:34.550 --> 34:35.551
- Mm.

34:35.595 --> 34:38.554
- So I'm here
to tell you a story.

34:39.816 --> 34:41.383
It's, um,

34:41.427 --> 34:46.171
it's a sad love story about
a man who has a beautiful home,

34:46.214 --> 34:48.651
beautiful family...

34:51.176 --> 34:54.527
A beautiful wife,
