36:08.166 --> 36:10.255
- Make it hurt.

36:15.651 --> 36:18.219
- My client had a long,
dark night of the soul

36:18.263 --> 36:19.568
to think about this.

36:19.612 --> 36:21.222
- Well, there's not
a whole lot to think about.

36:21.266 --> 36:22.919
