loved their husbands--

37:05.310 --> 37:06.398
they wouldn't sleep with you.

37:06.441 --> 37:07.747
- That's right.

37:07.790 --> 37:10.184
- But when they refused you,
you threw 'em in jail.

37:10.228 --> 37:12.491
