38:27.174 --> 38:28.436
- He's gonna be
in a world of pain

38:28.480 --> 38:30.960
till he's eligible
for Medicare.

38:31.004 --> 38:32.005
- Good work, Carisi.

38:32.048 --> 38:33.920
- Nah, it wasn't me,
it was Rollins.

38:33.963 --> 38:36.139
I don't know how she did it,
