39:54.304 --> 39:55.349
- Good.

39:55.393 --> 39:58.308
- You and Eddie--things okay?

39:58.352 --> 40:00.049
- Yeah.

40:00.093 --> 40:04.489
After you talked to Eddie,
before I agreed to testify,

40:04.532 --> 40:07.666
he and I talked a long time.

40:07.709 --> 40:11.452
He said he was so sad
what I had to go through,

40:11.496 --> 40:14.324
and how much he loved me.

40:14.368 --> 40:18.981
